{"tid":2337820,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"LiSA《鬼滅》主題曲點擊破一億","createTime":"2020-12-23T14:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T14:39:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"67b4897321afe0436001c73007533179c5fc05ce","tid":2337820,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:33:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201222/NCFKFQW2ZNG4TPEASMVWHZTU2U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201222%2FNCFKFQW2ZNG4TPEASMVWHZTU2U%2F&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=dad0cf74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201222%2FNCFKFQW2ZNG4TPEASMVWHZTU2U%2F&h=aa72f7fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201222/NCFKFQW2ZNG4TPEASMVWHZTU2U/</a><br />\n<br />\nLiSA《鬼滅》主題曲點擊破一億<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Za6KbU76gyMU3y2zfoO7I2QX0E8=/640x450/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L3OSBZQFZ5G2DHLDL5R2H66EKQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZa6KbU76gyMU3y2zfoO7I2QX0E8%3D%2F640x450%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL3OSBZQFZ5G2DHLDL5R2H66EKQ.jpg&h=11fdce7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《鬼滅之刃劇場版 無限列車篇》<br />\n<br />\n日本電影《鬼滅之刃劇場版 無限列車篇》在當地屢破紀錄，票房已累積311億日圓（約23.2億港元），差五億日圓（約3730港元）便取代《千與千尋》成為日本史上最賣座電影之首。<br />\n<br />\n電影大收旺場，連帶為電影版主唱主題曲《炎》的33歲動漫歌姬LiSA亦同樣受惠，不僅登上各大小排行榜冠軍，MV在YouTube突破一億次觀看紀錄，LiSA隨即拍片答謝大家支持，表示對此創舉感到難以置信。LiSA下月將推出新單曲《dawn》，她還為山崎賢人明年2月主演的新片《夏之門》唱主題曲《Surprise》，她會包辦填詞，是她首次為真人演出電影獻唱主題曲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TUIpBSG-WHKT3hXWLScpOPpHcu8=/640x500/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NWJTAJM3BVFVLCOXF3EMD47VLA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTUIpBSG-WHKT3hXWLScpOPpHcu8%3D%2F640x500%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNWJTAJM3BVFVLCOXF3EMD47VLA.jpg&h=e8cb754d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■LiSA日前拍片答謝動漫迷支持她主唱的《鬼滅》主題曲。"},{"pid":"748e013a61a0f735528689bcbcacd2278264f01c","tid":2337820,"uid":272819,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:35:41.000Z","msg":"差五億日圓（約3730港元"},{"pid":"cdaa055df8370c1e88343642a59b6f2ba39f728c","tid":2337820,"uid":193770,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:39:40.000Z","msg":"首歌係出色既"}]}